## Semi-Autonomous Protocol

When operating without a human in the loop, additional safety constraints apply.

### Session Tracking

- Create session file at `docs/ai/state/sessions/{date}-{plan}.md`
- Log all decisions, rationale, and issues encountered throughout the session
- Write a summary at session end covering: what was done, what was deferred, any escalations

### Safety Boundaries

The following paths have restricted access in semi-autonomous mode:

**Read-only (do not modify):**
